I'm here to help with whatever you need! Let me know your question, and I'll do my best to assist you right away.
why was my ad account jsut charged?

There could be a few reasons why your ad account was just charged. If you recently ran ads, the charge might be for the ad spend. Additionally, there is a temporary $10 card authorization fee that is held for 7 days and then refunded if not used. If you need more details or have any concerns, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com.
i don't remember running ads today, why was I charged?

If you don't remember running ads today, the charge might be related to the temporary $10 card authorization fee. This fee is held for 7 days and refunded if not used. If you believe this charge is incorrect or need further assistance, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com to dispute the billing issue.
